intent_template: Can you add {description} to my cart?
intent: Can you add enough of the cheapest uncrustable items that appeared in the video to be the same amount as the person in the video ordered to my cart?
intermediate_intent: What was the cheapest uncrustable items that appeared in the video? How many uncrustable items did the person in the video order?

instantiation_dict.description: enough of the cheapest uncrustable items that appeared in the video to be the same amount as the person in the video ordered

must_include: Smucker's Uncrustables Peanut Butter and Strawberry Jam Sandwiches, 2 Ounces (Pack of 4) (Frozen)
Smucker's Uncrustables Peanut Butter and Strawberry Jam Sandwiches, 2 Ounces (Pack of 4) (Frozen)

program_html.locator: lambda:(() => {try {return Array.from(document.querySelectorAll(".item-info")).find(el => el.textContent.includes("Smucker's Uncrustables Peanut Butter and Strawberry Jam Sandwiches, 2 Ounces (Pack of 4) (Frozen)")).querySelector("input").getAttribute("data-item-qty")} catch (e) {return " "}})()
